org.osmdroid.tileprovider.cachemanager

Class CacheManager.CacheManagerTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<Object,Integer,Integer>
      • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.cachemanager.CacheManager.CacheManagerTask
  • Enclosing class:
    CacheManager

    public static class CacheManager.CacheManagerTask
extends AsyncTask<Object,Integer,Integer>
    generic class for common code related to AsyncTask management - performing an action - within a manager - on a list of tiles (potentially sorted by ascending zoom level) - and with callbacks for task progression
